### **2. 25_ResponseTimeWatcher**  
**Description:**  
A lightweight script to ping URLs and log response time and status.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# ResponseTimeWatcher - API Ping Utility

ResponseTimeWatcher checks the latency and HTTP status of one or more endpoints and logs the result.

## Features
- Multi-URL support  
- Timeout handling  
- Clean console logging  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/25_ResponseTimeWatcher.git
cd 25_ResponseTimeWatcher
python monitor.py
